{"tid":1203390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple已有後備計劃　全數iPhone生產可搬離中國","createTime":"2019-06-11T12:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:39:47.000Z","uid":28114,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c22319cd004b1bc0946c04e2cf9fce5fa02c43f","tid":1203390,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:27:01.000Z","msg":"美國著名財經媒體彭博報道，蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)已準備好「後備計劃」，如果中美貿易戰惡化至失控，輸美的iPhone生產工序將全面撤出中國。 <br />\n<br />\n報道引述全球「代工」一哥台資機構鴻海高層指出，如有需要，在中國以外將有足夠的產能，生產全部iPhone。 <br />\n<br />\n目前情況是：若美國總統特朗普決定「晒冷」對中國餘下逾3,000億美元進口貨品徵收關稅，必然會涉及到蘋果公司的產品。 <br />\n<br />\n鴻海指出，若有需要因應中美貿易戰而調整生產的話，會全力支持蘋果公司。目前有25%產能位於中國以外，可以供給美國市場所需，再加上印度的投資，有足夠產能滿足需求。 <br />\n<br />\n鴻海強調，目前蘋果公司未作出任何指示。一旦有指示，將迅速反應。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190611/mobile/bkn-20190611183847368-0611_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190611%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190611183847368-0611_00842_001.html&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=0119e08c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190611/mobile/bkn-20190611183847368-0611_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"77219037f3d542cd2e355a146ad458b044d3dac0","tid":1203390,"uid":209386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"撤資gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55958118e7a6cf2cd8529e079462b9e1a8a860bd","tid":1203390,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:39:47.000Z","msg":"全力支持中國對抗美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔反抗正一無膽契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}